    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p><span style="line-height: 1.538em;">If you are reading this thinking you are going to get some helpful Drupal development or site building tips...sorry! As a marketing person who runs a hardcore Drupal development shop, I often relate more to our clients than our developers. I am sure there are often times when my team wants to clock me over the head with their MacBook Pros as I play the role of the client during internal discussions.The fact is, many of the folks who are working with Drupal are more like me than my developers.That is why they hire us.</span></p></div></div></div>
